Far into the skies that hung over the Dark Tower two dark figures seemed to almost drift lazily just off center from the sun. However with a startling swiftness they began to grow larger and larger as the sleek and powerful shape of Cyclonus and the Predatory presence of Scourge made thier way ever closer. Like dark shadows they cut through the air leaving only the barest whisper of a noise in their wake. 

As they approached, the leader of the two, Cyclonus, keyed his internal communications system, configuring it to the Predacon frequencies and codes, "Hydras" Cyclonus' familiar deep voice sounded out over the channel, "The time has come for us to meet once again. Respond."

<TAG: Hydras/Predacons>

Preston
(Cyclonus/Scourge)
